Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:12.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not often I can write on a ship, so this was a great experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:16.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I also found out that I can ease myself thinking I'm dirtying white paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:20.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The brushing is a lot easier now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:23.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just one more month until the Narukain Exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,With one month, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:35.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon{\i0}. ["pickles"]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This much?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If'n ya finish 'em, I'll bring some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So they do go out from the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's no way I can eat this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:00.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have to concentrate on calligraphy now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll write an innovative and artistic {\i1}konomon--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}konomon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Write... I'm going to write on the {\i1}konomon--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}konomon{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:14.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Konomon{\i0}-in Exhibit is next month--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}Konomon{\i0}-in Exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon. Konomon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:21.14,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Konomon"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Unnioegi"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}"Translation: Going to the sea to swim"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:03.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon. Konomon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:06.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon. Konomon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:12.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If'n ya finish 'em, I'll bring some more... more... more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:13.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konomon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Teach me calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's you girls...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"You girls"? That's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:29.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Grandpa told me to bring them, since ain't nothin' wrong with having them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, can you help with our subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,First, hold the brush with your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--This is my right hand!\N--Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You have to be right-handed to do calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:46.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, but it's easier to write with the hand closer to the inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And what's the subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... This.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:50.93,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Visiting Old, Learning New"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:54.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll write an example, so watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:04.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aww... You're not gonna slap it on like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:08.01,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Visiting Old, Learning New"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "slap it on"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everything starts with fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanna write 'em like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's flashy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah... That's still in the works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Once it's done and recognized,\NI'll teach it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:21.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Recognized by...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I get first place in next month's Narukain Exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're good enough without getting an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:34.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just wanna have fun writing without worrying 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Have fun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You girls are such kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, Naru. Write this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.18,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Cat"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yay! Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:50.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now that I'm teaching,\NI'll make sure you're both awarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:56.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,With results, you'll know firsthand why I'm so fixed on getting an award...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now, start writing for the next hour like there's no tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't ink your brush twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The line here is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop your brush once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't take this no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You girls! Stop being lazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:27.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You girls were the ones who asked for help on the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't let you take anything less than first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, but how many times are ya gonna make us write the same stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aren't there any tips for writing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you girls kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:40.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do you think professional calligraphers write beautiful characters easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Feel the emotions being written into a single piece of calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thousands upon thousands of our predecessors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:49.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,have written on paper millions upon millions of their emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Who?\N--Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:55.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Physical fatigue... Mental breakdown...\NConstant solitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, the limits. See the limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just a step... Just a step closer to completion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:09.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yet ahead is an eternal desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can't walk... You're tired of writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's at that moment you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...the god of calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:22.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But that god is also a mirage from the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone hallucinating on calligraphy before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:30.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We don't wanna reach that point over a simple middle school subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Before you go on, buy us some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You girls aren't into this after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We are! We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're into this, so please let us take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right, but you better be writing when I return!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei is really a calligraphy nut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,At this rate, he probably can't get a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:58.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe he's in a platonic relationship or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Lemme check the room out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop it, that's tasteless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe it's his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0}, just stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shucks, a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's with the interest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A commemorative picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe he's going out with one of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How 'bout her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She's good-looking, but she's not standing close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:26.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Isn't she rather plain to be Sensei's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't think looks matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's satisfied with anyone as long as they talk about calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:39.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You think any gal's gonna listen to his delusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:42.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Got it!\N--Anyone can listen, even monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--This.\N--What's the matter, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei said this was his treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--What's this?\N--A picture stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sure feels like he's got his "special someone" in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei was someone's wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:02.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru? You're using the word "wife" wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:05.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, Naru likes Sensei a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:11.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's weirder to have someone his age not go out with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:14.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait ten more years and you'll be prettier, Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:17.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go and plunder him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Plunder...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, let's have a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...at Sensei's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I bought some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:34.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Get serious, or else you're not even going to get an award!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, you're twenty-three already, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look at things other than calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whatcha thinking, fallin' in love with some historic figure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,C'mon back to reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, just go out with Naru already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:52.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Right! I'm gonna plunder you!\N--Plunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey! You! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,At this rate, you're gonna die alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Plunder!\N--What the heck are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:12.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The kids said they were going swimming, so I was hoping you could monitor them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:15.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I actually asked the Head Teacher, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go fishin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everyone can swim, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If it's just watching them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:27.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, but it looks like Miwa and\NTama are going with them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:31.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can you keep watch so that they don't mimic anything dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll have Hiroshi go along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Something is bound to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Sensei! Let's hurry up!\N--Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--C'mon, hurry!\N--Hey, wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Sensei, hurry, hurry!\N--I got it, I got it! Let me get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Butt...\N--Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Miwa-{\i1}nee{\i0} and Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiya, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're late, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:02.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with the gym suit-like wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not "like"--these {\i1}are{\i0} our gym suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:06.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's easier to swim in these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? You're swimming in those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It should be a pain swimming with your clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hm? Then you take yours off, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I don't have a swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,C'mon already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Hiro isn't here--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:30.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You ready, everyone? Follow Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:36.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's only thinking about playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!\NI'm gonna master backstroking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, don't go running around too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:51.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We go to the beach every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Beach? More like rocks, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Play somewhere safe, like a real beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A beach is where kids play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's where we should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The ground... is so slippery...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You city folks are such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:15.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:19.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He'll be fine. Everyone goes through this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right, jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Yeah!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Super huge!\N--Super huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sea urchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sea urchin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop it already, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hina! You found any fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, but my goggles were clouded, so I couldn't see well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then use mugwort to wipe 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I got some mugwort leaves in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The mugwort sap stops it from being cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow. Naru, you know so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're like a grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whatcha mean, "grandma"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoops, sorry. You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm only seven years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:20.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look at them kiddies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They don't know a thing about how to enjoy the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see ya! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiroshi Critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa! An octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I got 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're so cool, Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So uncool, Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look at them guys. They don't know how to enjoy the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0}. I'm a bit tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You okay? Don't overdo yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:06.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to go rest where Sensei is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:16.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay, Tama? Your face is all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:20.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm an indoor kind of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you're an indoor person, stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,First, water. Can you drink now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good, you're doin' great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is it...? I feel like she's staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:42.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Have you ever been troubled to the point where you couldn't sleep at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NIs something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:50.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, not so much bothering, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:54.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,To be blunt, what do you think about Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:57.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiro? Why all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--You ready?\N--What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:03.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Here... you go!\N--He's about my age and easy to talk with, so he is like a younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No... We're not that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's more like someone who just brings food over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:14.08,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Jitter" "Jitter"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:14.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In the first place, why is eyeglasses girl asking me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:20.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I get it...! She must like Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:24.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see. So that's why she's been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:29.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Somehow, she came to ask me for advice as an elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now, isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:37.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I should do my best to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiro's a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He pays attention and can cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's the sort that you don't come across too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's the perfect guy to go out with--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who do you think is the reason\NI'm having sleepless nights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm no fujoshi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Fujoshi? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's dangerous running...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sen... sei...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:12.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Look, Naru! A sea cucumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ew, I can't believe you can hold that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru, you try holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you can hold this, you're an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're so mean, Miwa-{\i1}nee{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't like ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It looks gross, but you'll be fine once you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:39.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's so pudgy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good. You're an adult now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0}? Where's Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:51.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--How much of a wimp are you?!\N--Looks like he's still out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good, then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go someplace more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Someplace fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:07.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yup! Someplace only for adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ugh, damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was out again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We better be going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:23.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Haven't eaten lunch yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:27.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone! Start packing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Aww... Is it already time?\N--I don't wanna... Still wanna play...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Knew this'd be difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Naru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,She was with Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0} a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Miwa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's dangerous! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:02.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Miwa, looks like\NSensei is sayin' something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really? Wonder if it's time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's jump once more, then go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:10.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, but before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:12.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:13.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:21.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop! Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good job! Now that's my young gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:49.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I geard Sensei cheerin' for me, sayin', "Naru!" when I gumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ghat's why I wasn't sghared at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Cheering?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:56.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess he was sayin' something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey... Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it! Doing such dangerous things...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:12.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We won't do it again, so cheer up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:13.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:37.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Until I came to this island, all I needed to do was think about myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:42.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've ever worried this much for someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:53.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! I won't make you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Me either!\N--Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! I won't do anything dangerous anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I won't ever do anything dangerous either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:07.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Sensei! Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Guess the outsider really got his roots in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't expect me to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:18.89,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Sigh"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.22,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Cool breeze"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Call received" "1 call"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"Kawafuji"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.58,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Fukue Airport"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's no good. He's not answering...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:50.08,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Out of area"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:48.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? Out of area again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Dang, what an inconvenient place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I like the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everything is like a miniature set. So tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kosuke, you're making fun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:06.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay... The "where" doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As long as I can meet Handa-{\i1}san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your hair's a wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:56.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Been super humid recently, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:58.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, you do have kinked hair to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:02.72,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Shaggy"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:03.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Found a colleague!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:05.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, you girls came to fish too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, your hair's quite something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:11.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Really? When I'm feeling good, it's usually like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nah, that's because of the humidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:18.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You both have similar hair types.\NPretty much the same cuts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:19.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't copy me, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Copy"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:23.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why not just crop it down short?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:26.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, it wouldn't match me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:29.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, got a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:31.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can Head Teacher join ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:35.28,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Shaggy-curly"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:35.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell ya, this humidity is such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:38.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The same as Head Teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:39.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank goodness I have straight hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:42.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Short hair isn't the thing, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:46.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}tengusa{\i0} head!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:50.93,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Tengusa" ["seaweed"]
